    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"resting\" just means sitting here in the dark waiting for the next wave to hit. it's not even peaceful, it's just exhausting. i feel like i'm just waiting for the pain to stop, but it never does. it's like i'm stuck in a loop of just... hurting. i just want it to be over. i just want the noise to stop.",
